					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p183407">Re: Introducing the VeriSNES (FPGA-based SNES)</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=183407#p183407"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Nov 24, 2016 3:51 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
